# .ignore — ripgrep ignore file consumed by opencode's grep/glob/list tools
# .gitignore already excludes most build outputs, secrets, and OS cruft.
# This file un-ignores paths that opencode SHOULD discover despite being in .gitignore,
# and excludes a few repo-specific dirs that add no search value.

# Un-ignore: these are gitignored but opencode should be able to find them
!.shellcheckrc
!.editorconfig
!.github/
!renovate.json

# Exclude: large generated/binary dirs with no useful text content
bench_output/
megalinter-reports/
docs/sessions/
